The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Bopanna, Mirnyi in title round
                                                                                                                                                                                                       Bopanna, Mirnyi in title round
          
	St Petersburg: Indias Rohan Bopanna and Belarussian partner Max Mirnyi reached the doubles final of the St Petersburg Open defeating Mikhail Mertinak of Slovakia and Lovro Zovko of Croatia 7-5, 6-2 here on Saturday.         
	In the final, the unseeded Indo-Belarusian pair will face Travis Parott of the US and Filip Polasek of Slovakia, who beat Mikhail Elgin and Alexandre Kudryavstev of Russia 7-5, 4-6, 10-6.         
	Earlier, Bopanna and Mirnyi overcame a second-set lapse to advance to the semi-finals. The duo tamed the pair of Igor Kunitsyn and Marat Safin 6-4, 3-6, 13-11 in one hour and 15 minutes.(AGENCIES)                                                                                                                          
